{"tid":1495471,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2013年8月19晶，陳雲貼","createTime":"2019-08-22T05:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T05:40:47.000Z","uid":125031,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7e1517461c991da9ad2630204d423a408dd906","tid":1495471,"uid":125031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"陳雲：香港不必鬧獨立，因為香港擁有的主權，比歐盟的一個成員國還要大。我們有獨立貨幣、財政獨立，北京的法令不能在香港執行。只是大家不察覺，也不去捍衛香港的自治權，令到香港變成殖民地的樣子。試問，香港如果無實然的主權（de facto sovereign），為何可以自行送走美國間諜斯諾登（當然其中有北京的意旨，但北京從無露面）？香港不遵守國際的引渡協定，獨自決定送走斯諾登。為什麼香港有這種權力？斯諾登事件的作用，就在證明香港的實然主權地位。<br />\n設想一下，如果《基本法》沒有2046年的限期，香港與中國的關係，就是邦聯關係，而即使有2046年的期限，影響也不大，當初歐洲共同體，就有不斷修訂彼此關係的期限。<br />\n香港要行使實然主權，所差的，只是雙普選。就是這麼簡單。這也是中共遲遲不願意放手的原因。然而，《基本法》如此訂立了，中共又能夠怎樣？除非民主黨代表港人意願，自己獻上違反普選的方案，替北京解套吧！<br />\n當初，英國在1997年之前，已經將香港弄到具備獨立的國際地位，之後才交還中國的，即是說，香港獨立的過程，是隱蔽住的漸進過程（implicit and progressive process），大家不會察覺。這是英國政治的高明之處，也是英國的苦心之處。"},{"pid":"b7c1eb94043788b581929e3541e04076a442a0b7","tid":1495471,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"借post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">前線以後噴漆<br />\n請噴英文！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. LIBERATE HK</span><br />\n<br />\n2. STAND WITH HK<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. GIVE ME DEMOCRACY OR GIVE ME DEATH</span><br />\n<br />\n4. CARRIE SOLD HK TO ChiNazi / XITLER<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">5. DEMOCRACY NOW</span><br />\n<br />\n6. #EYE4HK<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">7. END POLICE BRUTALITY NOW</span><br />\n<br />\n8. FIGHT FOR FREEDOM<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">9, HUMAN RIGHTS &amp; HK<br />\n DEMOCRACY ACT</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYeORRi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYeORRi.jpg&h=b97a4722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLiberate HK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> The Revolution of Our Times<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a58d11382846ac3a1561c7d5f4725d61b3af03f","tid":1495471,"uid":140326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:58:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝大台陳雲教路</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2013年 已經好有見地，走在最前線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168318ec842c194732e5f7afad303a77825521c2","tid":1495471,"uid":168359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fdd17bf438410031a28ce9476e2a10eda33d56","tid":1495471,"uid":125031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"國師係堅勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651b389af5dcd0d4dc815fa6ab95e26f3a99dd8c","tid":1495471,"uid":6870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c03492f55acf5c44d6074a69751c20961deb8a","tid":1495471,"uid":195409,"like":0,"dislike"